response.overview: Dr Kamdev kumar is a sexologist & counsellor. He starts this institute in the name of “Romance Training Institute” in which any sex and romance problem will be solved. They hire a girl name Mishti, who brings her boyfriend also as a trainer. 4 couples come who has some or the other problems. How Mishti tries to solve the problems of each couples. For this watch Doctor Kamdev.
response.title: Doctor Kamdev
